      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties derived from certified coupon testing of production-lot Ti-6Al-4V; geometric inputs from calibrated CMM measurements of test articles.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus were characterised from tensile coupon tests (n=5) of the same production lot as the pedicle screw test articles. Geometric dimensions were measured on each of the 11 test constructs using a calibrated coordinate measuring machine (CMM uncertainty ±3 µm). Input uncertainty propagation documented in uncertainty budget UB-COU1-2026."
