      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative screws and UHMWPE blocks were tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A n=6, Lab B n=5). Lot traceability confirmed. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness was 3.1%, within the 5% threshold. Required level 3 achieved."
