      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions, loading protocol, and geometry are demonstrably equivalent to the physical test setup; equivalency documented with traceability to test records.",
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions (pin-roller, 10° offset per F1717 §8.1) and displacement-controlled loading rate (5 mm/min) in the FEA match the physical test setup exactly. Geometry was imported from the same CAD files used for manufacturing. Equivalency matrix documented in EM-COU1-2026 with traceability to test laboratory setup photographs and fixture calibration records."
    },
